reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Thr Best laundry soap out there.!!!!!!
reviews.reviewText: Prepare to be whisked away on a sensory journey where cleanliness meets pure, unadulterated joy. Gain laundry pods aren't just a laundry detergent; they're a ticket to an olfactory paradise, a utopia where your clothes emerge not just clean but infused with a scent that whispers, "I've got my life together."First off, let's talk efficiency, because in this fast-paced world, who has the time to measure liquid detergent? Gain pods are the epitome of convenience—just toss one in with your load, and voilà, you're practically a laundry wizard. It's like they were designed for those of us who consider 'adulting' a sport and are in it to win it.But the real MVP here is the scent. Oh, the scent! It's as if Gain managed to bottle the essence of a spring morning, a dash of happiness, and a sprinkle of sunshine into each pod. Your clothes come out of the wash not just clean, but also carrying an aroma that could practically double as a mood enhancer. It's the kind of scent that makes you want to bury your face in your laundry and take a deep breath, reassuring you that everything's going to be alright in the world.Durability? You bet. These pods pack a punch, cutting through dirt and grime like it's nobody's business, leaving your fabrics fresh, clean, and ready to face another day. Whether it's the aftermath of a mud-soaked adventure or just the daily grind, Gain has got you covered.In summary, Gain laundry pods are not just a laundry essential; they're a lifestyle choice. For those who value efficiency, crave divine scents, and demand the best for their fabrics, look no further. Gain pods are here to elevate your laundry game to levels of satisfaction you never thought possible.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Love the smell
reviews.reviewText: Gain Flings Laundry Detergent Soap Pacs, HE Compatible, have been a game-changer in my laundry routine. These little pacs pack a powerful cleaning punch while being incredibly convenient to use.The HE compatibility is a big plus, as it ensures they work efficiently in my high-efficiency washer. The scent of these detergent pacs is delightful; my clothes come out of the wash smelling fresh and clean, which is a huge bonus.What I appreciate most is the mess-free aspect. No more measuring or spills – just toss in a pac and let it do its magic. The cleaning performance is generally excellent, even on tough stains, although some heavily soiled items may require pre-treatment.The only downside is that the cost can add up compared to traditional liquid detergents. However, for the convenience and effectiveness they offer, I find it well worth it. Gain Flings have become a staple in my laundry room, making the chore of washing clothes much more manageable and leaving my clothes looking and smelling fantastic. Highly recommended for anyone looking to simplify their laundry routine without sacrificing cleanliness and freshness!
